  <div class="ll-modal-content">
    <button class="ll-modal-close" id="ll-terms-modal-close-btn">&times;</button>
    <h3 class="ll-modal-title">Accuracy & Terms of Use</h3>
    <div class="ll-modal-body">
      <p>This spoke calculator is a professional-grade tool provided for your convenience. LoamLabs has made every reasonable effort to ensure the accuracy of the component data and the underlying calculation formulas.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Component Variations:</strong> For absolute precision, always measure your components yourself.</li>
        <li><strong>ERD is Critical:</strong> A 1mm error in ERD results in a 0.5mm error in spoke length.</li>
        <li><strong>Nipple Washers:</strong> Be mindful of whether your ERD measurement includes nipple washer thickness.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>By using this tool, you agree that it is your responsibility to verify all measurements. LoamLabs is not liable for any costs incurred from incorrect spoke length calculations.</strong></p>
      <div class="ll-disclaimer-actions" style="margin-top: 2rem; justify-content: center;">
        <button id="ll-terms-modal-ok-btn" class="ll-button-primary">OK</button>
      </div>
